      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the profound pain in your desire to see your loved ones live full, worry-free lives without the burden of your care. While your feelings of guilt are deeply human, they do not reflect the reality that their sacrifice is a testament to their love and dedication during your time of need. Please consider discussing these specific worries with a geriatric care manager or a therapist who specializes in aging-in-place, as they can connect you with resources that provide hands-on support to lighten their load.",
