      "role": "user",
      "content": "i suppose, but love doesn't give them their time back. i just feel like i'm taking up space that could be better used for their own families and kids. it's like i'm just stuck in the way of their happiness. i wonder if they'd actually be relieved if they didn't have to deal with all this anymore.",
